גַן);","strongs_def":"a satire","kjv_def":"music."},"H4486":{"id":"H4486","lemma":"מַנְדַּע","translit":"mandaʻ","pron":"man-dah'","derivation":"(Aramaic) corresponding to H4093 (מַדָּע);","strongs_def":"wisdom or intelligence","kjv_def":"knowledge, reason, understanding.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"knowledge(2x), reason(1x), understanding(1x)"},"H4487":{"id":"H4487","lemma":"מָנָה","translit":"mânâh","pron":"maw-naw'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"properly, to weigh out; by implication, to allot or constitute officially; also to enumerate or enroll","kjv_def":"appoint, count, number, prepare, set, tell.","pos":"verb","usage":"number(14x), prepare(5x), appointed(4x), tell(3x), count(1x), set(1x)"},"H4488":{"id":"H4488","lemma":"מָנֶה","translit":"mâneh","pron":"maw-neh'","derivation":"from H4487 (מָנָה);","strongs_def":"properly, a fixed weight or measured amount, i.e. (techn.) a maneh or mina","kjv_def":"maneh, pound.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"pound(4x), maneh(1x)"},"H4489":{"id":"H4489","lemma":"מֹנֶה","translit":"môneh","pron":"mo-neh'","derivation":"from H4487 (מָנָה);","strongs_def":"properly, something weighed out, i.e. (figuratively) a portion of time, i.e. an instance","kjv_def":"time.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"times(2x)"},"H4490":{"id":"H4490","lemma":"מָנָה","translit":"mânâh","pron":"maw-naw'","derivation":"from H4487 (מָנָה);","strongs_def":"properly, something weighed out, i.e. (generally) a division; specifically (of food) a ration; also a lot","kjv_def":"such things as belonged, part, portion.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"portion(10x), part(3x), belonged(1x)"},"H4491":{"id":"H4491","lemma":"מִנְהָג","translit":"minhâg","pron":"min-hawg'","derivation":"from H5090 (נָהַג);","strongs_def":"the driving (of a chariot)","kjv_def":"driving."},"H4492":{"id":"H4492","lemma":"מִנְהָרָה","translit":"minhârâh","pron":"min-haw-raw'","derivation":"from H5102 (נָהַר);","strongs_def":"properly, a channel or fissure, i.e. (by implication) a cavern","kjv_def":"den.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"den(1x)"},"H4493":{"id":"H4493","lemma":"מָנוֹד","translit":"mânôwd","pron":"maw-node'","derivation":"from H5110 (נוּד)","strongs_def":"a nodding or toss (of the head in derision)","kjv_def":"shaking.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"shaking(1x)"},"H4494":{"id":"H4494","lemma":"מָנוֹחַ","translit":"mânôwach","pron":"maw-no'-akh","derivation":"from H5117 (נוּחַ);","strongs_def":"quiet, i.e. (concretely) a settled spot, or (figuratively) a home","kjv_def":"(place of) rest.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"rest(7x)"},"H4495":{"id":"H4495","lemma":"מָנוֹחַ","translit":"Mânôwach","pron":"maw-no'-akh","derivation":"the same as H4494 (מָנוֹחַ); rest;","strongs_def":"Manoach, an Israelite","kjv_def":"Manoah.","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Manoah(18x)"},"H4496":{"id":"H4496","lemma":"מְנוּחָה","translit":"mᵉnûwchâh","pron":"men-oo-khaw'","derivation":"or מְנֻחָה; feminine of H4495 (מָנוֹחַ);","strongs_def":"repose or (adverbially) peacefully; figuratively, consolation (specifically, matrimony); hence (concretely) an abode","kjv_def":"comfortable, ease, quiet, rest(-ing place), still.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"rest(15x), comfortable(1x), ease(1x), quiet(1x), still(1x)"},"H4497":{"id":"H4497","lemma":"מָנוֹן","translit":"mânôwn","pron":"maw-nohn'","derivation":"from H5125 (נוּן);","strongs_def":"a continuator, i.e. heir","kjv_def":"son.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"son(1x)"},"H4498":{"id":"H4498","lemma":"מָנוֹס","translit":"mânôwç","pron":"maw-noce'","derivation":"from H5127 (נוּס);","strongs_def":"a retreat (literally or figuratively); abstractly, a fleeing","kjv_def":"[idiom] apace, escape, way to flee, flight, refuge.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"refuge(4x), apace(1x), escape(1x), flight(1x)"},"H4499":{"id":"H4499","lemma":"מְנוּסָה","translit":"mᵉnûwçâh","pron":"men-oo-saw'","derivation":"or מְנֻסָה; feminine of H4498 (מָנוֹס);","strongs_def":"retreat","kjv_def":"fleeing, flight.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"flight(1x), fleeing(1x)"}}